---
title: Thai-Style Chicken Burger with Pickled Cucumber Salad and Sweet Potato Wedges
description: The HelloFresh twist in this recipe is our Thai-style blend, which lends a kick to these juicy chicken burgers. It contains flakes of small-but-potent bird's eye chilli alongside gingery galangal, fragrant Thai basil and the citrus notes of lemongrass. Time to get tongue-Thai-ed!
